	<p>
	  <lb n="1"/>
	  therānaṃ 
	  <app><lem>bhaṃ</lem><rdg source="#AS #CTI">bha</rdg
	    ></app>yaṃta-<persName key="pers:Indradeva"
	    >i<unclear>ṃ</unclear>dadevasa</persName>
	  hathi ca puvādo hathinaṃ ca uparimā hethimā ca veyikā dānaṃ
        </p>
      </div>
      <div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
	<p>
	  The elephants and, before the elepehants, the rail-mouldings
	  above and below (are) the gift of the Sthavira, 
	  the venerable
	  <persName key="pers:Indradeva">Indradeva</persName>.
	</p>
